
---

## ⚙️ 2. `.gitattributes`

Create at:
`~/rstudio-tier-setup/.gitattributes`

```gitattributes
# Normalize text files to LF line endings for Linux systems
* text=auto eol=lf

# Treat scripts as text
*.sh text
*.py text
*.R text

# Preserve binary assets
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico binary

# Documentation
*.md text diff=markdown
*.yaml text
*.yml text

# Ignore CRLF normalization for Docker layers
*.tar binary
*.img binary
*.sif binary
